### [LOCAL] Listar todas as companhias (Rotas GET costumam ser públicas!)
GET http://localhost:3000/companie HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### [PRODUCAO] Listar todas as companhias
GET https://uc13-projeto-2xiu.onrender.com/companie HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Filtrar pelo atributo nome
GET http://localhost:3000/companie?name=SENAC HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Filtrar pelo CNPJ
GET http://localhost:3000/companie?cnpj=03709814005157 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Filtrar por lugares (places)
GET http://localhost:3000/companie?places=EPISCOPAL HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

### Mostrar uma única companhia (por ID)
GET http://localhost:3000/companie/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json  

### Editar a companhia (ID de exemplo - Requer Token)
PUT http://localhost:3000/companie/1 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI>

{
    "name": "SERVICO NACIONAL DE APRENDIZAGEM INDUSTRIAL SENAI",          
    "places": "RUA ANTONIO MICUCCI 350",      
    "fundaments": "ESTUDOS INDUSTRIAIS",    
    "methods": "ENSINO MEDIO E TECNICO"         
}

### Deletar a companhia (Requer Token)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/companie/2 HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <COLE_SEU_TOKEN_AQUI>
